    <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">An opportunity presents itself for engaging in activities that operate outside the boundaries of legality. <strong>Kidnappings</strong>, <strong>robberies</strong>, <strong>thefts</strong>, <strong>war for business</strong>, <strong>arms trade</strong>. You have the freedom to fully immerse yourself in the role of a mafia member, whether it be portraying a tough and resolute individual or one who is compassionate and just. The choice is entirely yours, and the paths available are plentiful.</span></p>
    <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">In total, 4 mafias can be found in the state: <strong>Russian Mafia</strong>, <strong>Yakuza</strong>, <strong>La Cosa Nostra</strong>, <strong>Armenian Mafia</strong>. Some of them may be in an alliance and some of them may fight hard among themselves.</span></p>
    <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">One of the main tasks of every mafia - <strong>control of the largest number of businesses in the state</strong>, for one business under the control of the mafia, they receive <em>90</em>$. Also to all <strong>mafias need</strong>&nbsp;to actively fight against state organizations, preventing them from supplying materials and medicines, and subsequently taking them for themselves.</span></p>
    <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Illegal items that help in robberies, kidnappings and other criminal cases, the bandits will be able to buy on "<strong>black market</strong>"</span></p>
    <p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Recruitment</strong> Within the mafia, individuals are required to submit applications, and if you aspire to become a part of it, it is crucial to bear in mind that full compliance with the organization's internal rules is mandatory.</span></p>
